parameters: You find the note Jay hid in the sewers.
Quaint as hell, I'll have to look into it."
You saw the shadow of a flying thing
Too distorted to be a beast..
Some thing is taken away from your body
Your vision is blurred, and body is heavier..
You thought it was a man until you see it whole
Gibbous red organ-like stuff replaces its face
but you managed to run away.
You find a small jug of liquor hidden under a tree.
There is a page of newspaper stuck in a bush.
"Limuru village is facing the biggest population loss in its history,
Missing persons perhaps the main reason for it?"
